{"tid":1471219,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[長文]認真分析未來要做既事","createTime":"2019-08-14T08:18:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T08:32:44.000Z","uid":255194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f1ae53ef819c64b34a17260bcd3186a90427be33","tid":1471219,"uid":255194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T08:18:51.000Z","msg":"有d長，但希望大家睇晒佢<br />\n<br />\n經過兩個幾月既抗爭<br />\n大家應該都要睇清一樣野<br />\n<strong><ins>上面已經放手比警犬處理一切問題</ins></strong><br />\n所以，我地已經冇辦法從談判入手<br />\n和理抗爭已經不合時宜<br />\n革命先係現在唯一既出路<br />\n<br />\n要成功<br />\n首先我地要搵到對策<br />\n「上面已經放手比警犬處理一切問題」<br />\n可以拆解為兩個部分<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">上面點解會放手 </span></span> 同 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">警權無限大</span></span><br />\n<br />\n上面係指<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>中共</strong></span>，唔係林鄭政府<br />\n林鄭唔係一個話到事既人<br />\n如果佢話到事<br />\n簡單回應五大訴求已經足以解決問題<br />\n問題係中共唔肯讓步<br />\n佢要你地香港人經過今次<br />\n以後都唔敢再掂政治<br />\n但點解佢到今時今日剩係出把口<br />\n出埋d陰招<br />\n而唔係出解放軍呢？<br />\n<em><ins><strong>因為中共真係有壓力<br />\n一黎外國勢力睇撚住件事唔敢用自己個名鎮壓<br />\n二黎唔想咁多大陸人掂呢件事</strong></ins></em><br />\n所以先會放手比香港警察處理<br />\n自己處於觀望態度<br />\n<br />\n然後警察被賦予既權力愈黎愈大<br />\n球證、旁證、主辦、協辦單位都係上面既人<br />\n製造白色恐怖就係咁簡單<br />\n不過前提係<br />\n<em><ins><strong>要警察捉到人件事先可以暢順運作<br />\n只要冇左警察呢道防線<br />\n港共政府猶如空殼 任我地魚肉</strong></ins></em><br />\n除非解放軍出動<br />\n<br />\n所以未來既<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>重點</strong></span>就係<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>一、擊破香港警隊，重拾主導權<br />\n<br />\n二、逼使中共強硬表態，繼而逼使外國勢力主動介入</ins></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>一、擊破香港警隊，重拾主導權</ins></strong><br />\n香港警察三萬人<br />\n出黎遊行既香港人二百萬<br />\n條數點計都係贏<br />\n偏偏有決心上前線既可能一萬人都冇<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">要擊破就要智取 由內而外</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n戰術既野我唔多了解 唔多講<br />\n但基本野一定要做到<br />\n要贏就要全世界都能夠各施其職<br />\n因為今次活動冇大台<br />\n組織同資訊都十分混亂<br />\n所以今日起麻煩搵人<strong>組隊</strong><br />\n8至12人 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>準備好通訊器材</strong></span> 同 <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>溝通訊號</strong></span><br />\n起碼3個人做哨<br />\n去附近站崗 同埋 mon住直播tg發生咩事<br />\n隨時同前線互通消息<br />\n最好每隊都有一至兩個醫療兵跟隊<br />\n可以隨時救援<br />\n前線需要壯丁<br />\n女仔唔好隨便上 <br />\n因為戰力黎講你地幾乎係負數<br />\n除非你有操過 唔係只會陀衰家<br />\n但女仔唔係冇用<br />\n去考急救牌 幫手傳遞訊息同物資<br />\n好多野都需要你地幫手<br />\n如果有專業人士可以做到裝備/技術上升級更佳<br />\n總之要做到<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">一個小隊可以各方面都照顧到自己</span></span></strong><br />\n一切成形之後就可以多d聯合其他小隊<br />\n先可以配合唔同戰術擊破警隊<br />\n<br />\n再黎就係<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">禍必及妻兒</span></strong></span>既部分<br />\n識警犬既麻煩踴躍報料比老豆搵仔tg<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/Dadfindboy\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FDadfindboy&d=SW1PDOKa3sbtYTDDPfmX3eTO5ApsLFANoEfWU0iq%2Bkc%3D&h=15956f86\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/Dadfindboy</a><br />\n搵完仔自行組隊<br />\n好多巴打都有出post教點玩<br />\n我都唔再多講<br />\n<br />\n【我地仲忍乜】全面清洗狗竇．禍必先及妻兒！！！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1448109\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1448109</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>二、逼使中共強硬表態，繼而逼使外國勢力主動介入</ins></strong><br />\n呢個先係我重點想講既部分<br />\n有睇上文都知中共係買我地怕<br />\n加上自己經濟爆緊煲<br />\n<em><ins><strong><span style=\"color: green;\">香港問題上面行錯一步<br />\n都會被外國制裁到永不超生</span></strong></ins></em><br />\n我地雖不能夠旨意外國會提供軍火支援<br />\n但香港的而且確係美國一張用黎要脅中國既牌<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><em><ins>美國一日唔郁<br />\n現時香港既局勢無論點發展</ins></em></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">解放軍都係唔會出動住 </span></span><br />\n所以我地更加要趁現在部署得更詳盡<br />\n免得他朝有一日美國同中國達成協議<br />\n大部分香港人仲係on99唸住和平抗爭<br />\n到時真係大家一鑊熟 香港人被滅絕<br />\n<br />\n之後我想講既大家未必岩聽<br />\n但絕對要比d空間唸下<br />\n綜合以上觀點<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">我認為成個文宣方向要改變<br />\n由向外國求助轉為<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><ins>燒上大陸</span></ins></span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n點解中共依家開始係央視大造文章<br />\n老屈香港人？<br />\n<em><strong>因為中共知道要<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">革命</span></span> <br />\n單靠香港一個小城市係做唔到</strong></em><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong><em>但佢驚網上消息再傳落去<br />\n會愈黎愈多大陸人知道真相<br />\n最後會演變到全國都知</em></strong></span><br />\n大陸人咁齊心<br />\n好多時都因為佢地接收既係錯誤既資訊<br />\n<strong><em>大陸人同香港人對立其實係</em></strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">不必要</span></strong></span><br />\n係中共想見到既野黎<br />\n但當我地吹風吹到全個中國<br />\n都變左香港依家咁 二元對立 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><ins><strong><em>其實會對中共管治帶來好大既危機</em></strong></ins></span><br />\n之前武漢既事我其實都有出post講過下<br />\n有興趣可以睇下成個post同留言<br />\n我好比心機覆嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港人自己都未搞掂仲理武漢？<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1286937\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1286937</a><br />\n<br />\n當時既風向係認為大陸既事唔關香港事<br />\n不過真係想你地<strong>搞清楚真正既敵人</strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>唔係警察 唔係林鄭</strong></span><br />\n係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">中國共產黨</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n佢地驚既 <em><ins>ie 政權被動搖</ins></em><br />\n就要做<br />\n佢地想既 <em><ins>eg 內部分化</ins></em><br />\n就要停<br />\n當自己係反叛期既死𡃁仔<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><ins>發生任何事第一件事都要唸 <br />\n中共想唔想呢件事發生？</ins></strong></span></span><br />\n然後就死jer住黎做<br />\n咁樣就唔會再有<br />\n散水黨 和理非 勇武 左膠<br />\n互屌既情況<br />\n因為大家都目標一致 對準政權<br />\n<br />\n至於要點做<br />\n都係由內而外<br />\n係香港 趁仲有大陸黎旅行<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: green;\">擺多d街站</span></strong><br />\n捉住佢地黎講<br />\n甚至可以用佢地最鐘意既套路<br />\n姐係埋黎睇睇有野送 黎吸引佢地<br />\n<br />\n自己有親戚係大陸人<br />\n多d sd文宣、片比佢地睇 <br />\n網軍可以瘋狂上微博、bilibili等等洗版<br />\n開ac inbox人去明星度留言<br />\nblock一貼十<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">記得要用親切有耐性既態度同佢地溝通</span></strong></span><br />\n方法可以參考徐緣之前出既藍絲攻略<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/347912661973385/posts/2179701742127792?s=1474691662&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F347912661973385%2Fposts%2F2179701742127792%3Fs%3D1474691662%26sfns%3Dmo&d=SW1PDOKa3sbtYTDDPfmX3eTO5ApsLFANoEfWU0iq%2Bkc%3D&h=aef8e251\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/347912661973385/posts/2179701742127792?s=1474691662&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n <br />\n對外就要<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">係中國以外地區聯合其他人</span></strong></span><br />\n好似澳州大學有人搞連濃牆咁<br />\n將訊息傳比當地旅行/留學既大陸人睇<br />\n如果有識人做<strong><span style=\"color: green;\">酒店/hostel/民宿</span></strong><br />\n叫佢地幫手塗毒佢地<br />\n想再有系統d<br />\n叫佢地幫手搵d潛在反共人士 <br />\n以便裡應外合，互相照應<br />\n台灣係一個好適合做呢件事既地方<br />\n不過中共快先一步<br />\n已經限制左大陸人入境<br />\n可想而知佢地幾驚有呢d連動<br />\n<br />\n打左咁多 唔係幾識收尾<br />\n都係果句<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人自己要做好思想覺悟<br />\n清楚自己面對緊咩敵人<br />\n先會有勝算</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n歡迎理性討論"},{"pid":"4e0acccc0e948f5b8c8a1259999d035429aa29a8","tid":1471219,"uid":255194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T08:19:11.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a14920332b278ef1116c3faed8cde2235668416b","tid":1471219,"uid":255194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T08:19:32.000Z","msg":"求下大家睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cea03e96fc07bd917595e30c12fbfd797c9ac22d","tid":1471219,"uid":255194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T08:20:10.000Z","msg":"有咩唸錯請指出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f08b853ec8913fabf6cbca5f04edbfae1d0314c2","tid":1471219,"uid":255194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T08:21:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1640cee114f10459e730f4e2ad858d199b8d72a0","tid":1471219,"uid":255194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T08:22:19.000Z","msg":"pish<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98d88c04d11d3c8c64ab8792350dc3ecaf170b5c","tid":1471219,"uid":255194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T08:23:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"964a5d6231cbb85c36902094a71505583da349ac","tid":1471219,"uid":255194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T08:25:44.000Z","msg":"推阿推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4167ad90826ce42e55b3ab611cce61a95a2fb15","tid":1471219,"uid":255194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T08:26:34.000Z","msg":"唔好歧視p牌仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57788ef86fe4840922c1260042e78e57432edd22","tid":1471219,"uid":255194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T08:28:56.000Z","msg":"有冇人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0c545b499adb3a2f4f1950a0a83daf8bfd2070c","tid":1471219,"uid":255194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T08:29:34.000Z","msg":"推到大家收工睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b39fa19b0c35b6692085a91d9dc4d615373b219","tid":1471219,"uid":255194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T08:30:44.000Z","msg":"係咪標題改得差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa98d78a199c84ab8f818912d03295d2831b3b5f","tid":1471219,"uid":255194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T08:31:05.000Z","msg":"毒撚冇人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8fa570904f9a7cd2143688a9528d3fe1678e490","tid":1471219,"uid":255194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T08:32:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}